videos.description: Desi Rodriguez nails a deep 3-pointer to push Seton Hall's lead.
videos.headline: Rodriguez hits from deep for Seton Hall

videos.description: Angel Delgado scores in the post within an and-1 to increase the lead for the Pirates early in the first half
videos.headline: Delgado with a post move bucket for and-1

videos.description: Angel Delgado's steal and pass leads to Myles Cale transition dunk for the Pirates.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_Final Game Highlight Seton Hall (Delgado and Cale connect for fast-break dunk) 2017/11/15

videos.headline: Delgado and Cale connect for fast-break dunk

videos.description: Seton Hall's Myles Powell pump fakes Indiana's Devonte Green and then makes a 3.
videos.headline: Powell pump fakes and hits 3-pointer

videos.description: Desi Rodriguez takes on two Indiana defenders and scores with the left hand to extend the lead for Seton Hall.
videos.headline: Rodriguez drives and finishes with left-hand layup

videos.description: Indiana's Devonte Green is carrying his shoe while on defense and somehow picks Khadeen Carrington's pocket.
videos.headline: Green puts his shoe to good use

videos.description: Seton Hall's Angel Delgado scores on a drop step move and gets and-1.
videos.headline: Delgado's scores and-1 for Seton Hall

videos.description: Desi Rodriguez steals Indiana's Robert Johnson's pass and scores a fast-break layup for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Rodriguez rumbles for layup off steal

videos.description: Khadeen Carrington sends a bounce pass to Ismael Sanogo who scores with a reverse layup finish for Seton Hall.
videos.headline: Carrington dishes to Sanogo with a reverse lay up
